{"article_id":"8D58oD2dEJ1gOPfL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The US and Russia came significantly closer to a direct clash over Syria on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"when Donald Trump fired off an incendiary tweet","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that told Moscow to \" get ready \" for incoming US missiles ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"which the Russian military has vowed to shoot down .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"A standoff over a poison gas attack on a rebel-held suburb of Damascus on Saturday has since spiraled into the most dangerous confrontation between the two nuclear-armed powers since the height of the cold war ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"driven by Vladimir Putin ' s uncompromising backing for the Assad regime in Damascus and the volatility of the US president .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"\" Russia vows to shoot down any and all missiles","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"fired at Syria , \"","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"the US president tweeted .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" Get ready Russia ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"because they will be coming ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"nice and new and ' smart ! '","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"You shouldn ' t be partners with a Gas Killing Animal","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"who kills his people","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and enjoys it ! \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Trump 's Russia tweets show how misinformation can lead to global crisis","depth":3},{"id":16,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"\" We do not participate in Twitter diplomacy , \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Peskov was quoted as saying by Interfax .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"\" We support serious approaches .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"We continue to believe","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that it is important not to take steps","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that could harm an already fragile situation . \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Despite the president ' s menacing tweet ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"both the White House spokeswoman , Sarah Sanders , and the defence secretary , James Mattis , suggested","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"a decision on military action was still pending .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" All options are on the table","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"and a final decision hasn ' t been made , \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Mattis said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the US was \" still assessing intelligence \" on Saturday ' s attack on Douma ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"before attending a White House meeting of military and intelligence chiefs","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"chaired by Vice-President Mike Pence .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"In anticipation of an attack , Syrian planes had been flown to three Russian airbases","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"and senior Syrian government officials had been moved to safe houses in Damascus ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"according to sources in Turkey .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"A US naval battlegroup","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"- including the guided missile destroyer USS Donald Cook , and mostly likely a cruise missile submarine , USS Georgia -","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"was in place in the eastern Mediterranean on Wednesday night .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Play Video 0:58","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"White House struggles to explain Trump 's Russia missile tweet","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"- video","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"France has a missile ship , the Aquitaine , in the eastern Mediterranean and Rafale fighters","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"armed with cruise missiles in Jordan and Abu Dhabi .","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"President Emmanuel Macron has declared","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"that proven Syrian regime responsibility for chemical weapons use would cross a red line for France .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"In London , Theresa May summoned her cabinet for an emergency meeting on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to discuss the next steps ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"after warning","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that the Douma attack , \" could not go unchallenged \" .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"MPs are not due to return to Westminster from their Easter recess until next week ;","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"but the prime minister is under pressure","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to decide","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"whether the UK will join coordinated military action .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Speak","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"ng on Wednesday ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"ay pointed the finger at the Assad government ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"nd promised to ensure","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"hat those responsible were \" held to account \" .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"The use of chemical weapons can not go unchallenged , \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"We ' re rapidly reaching an understanding of what happened on the ground .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"ll the indications are","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"hat the Syrian regime was responsible . \"","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"t is not entirely clear what sparked Trump ' s 7am tweet ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"ut it came","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"fter news reports quoted the Russian ambassador to Lebanon , Alexander Zasypkin ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"arning","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"hat Russian forces in Syria would intercept any incoming US missiles ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"nd return fire at their source ,","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"ikely to mean US planes or ships .","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"ussian air defence did not try to shoot down US Tomahawk cruise missiles the last time","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"rump ordered punitive strikes","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"ollowing a chemical weapons attack","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"ttributed to the Assad regime .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"ut the Russian chief of general staff , Valery Gerasimov , warned last month","depth":11},{"i